[normal]Matters were left very unsatisfactorily in 2010 
[normal]with the suggestion that my clients somehow represented a threat to the operation of democracy in Sark.  Indeed this has affected the media's perception of events on Sark ever since.
[normal]By contrast, 
[normal]my clients regard themselves as v
[normal]indicated by events since 2010 and hope that this will be reflected in your forthcoming report, which should itself take the opportunity to redress the balance of your one-sided report of 2010.
[normal]A number of important points emerged from Lord McNally's recent evidence to your committee on 5 November
